    <div id="sect28">
      <h3>What are the shape icons for anonymous users?</h3>
      <p>Each anon user is assigned a unique "Anonicon" so that if several anonymous posters contribute to a thread, other user's can distinguish between the replies. Also, they're just fun!</p>
